<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset - {{shopName}}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
<header style="background-color: {{primaryColor}}; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
    <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="{{shopName}} Logo" style="max-width: 200px;">
</header>

<main style="padding: 20px;">
    <h2>Hello {{customerName}},</h2>

    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your {{shopName}} account. If you didn't make this request, please ignore this email.</p>

    <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
        <a href="{{resetPasswordUrl}}" style="background-color: {{secondaryColor}}; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Reset Your Password</a>
    </div>

    <p>This link will expire in {{expirationTime}} hours. If you need to request a new password reset, please visit our website and use the "Forgot Password" option.</p>

    <p>If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:</p>

    <p style="word-break: break-all;">{{resetPasswordUrl}}</p>

    <p>If you didn't request a password reset, please contact our support team immediately.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The {{shopName}} Team</p>
</main>

<footer style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.8em;">
    <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{shopName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
        <a href="{{shopUrl}}">Visit Our Store</a> |
        <a href="{{privacyPolicyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a>
    </p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>